This paper proposes a technique for predicting probabilities in machine learning classifiers, which is a common problem in many sub-fields of computer science. The paper focuses on optimizing a ranking loss, which is a technique used in machine learning for ranking problems. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
